---
// About section component
---

<div class="py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-6">
        About Me
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        becoming a unicorn person before a unicorn founder.
      </p>
    </div>
    
        <!-- Photo Left, Journey Text Right -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start mb-16">
      <!-- Profile Photo -->
      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
        <div class="w-48 h-60 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg bg-white dark:bg-primary-800 p-1">
          <img 
            src="/images/noah-photo.jpg" 
            alt="Noah Barbaros" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg scale-150 object-top"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Journey Text -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-6">
          My Journey
        </h3>
        <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          hey! if we haven't met before; i'm Noah, a 17 y/o obsessed with learning and "figuring it out". i don't have my life mapped out. i know what i like, and what i don't like, and i'm very biased towards action for things i like.
        </p>
        <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 leading-relaxed">
          what i love, is entrepreneurship -- and right now, i'm exploring everything there is to it -- head first.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Three Wide Cards Below -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Current Obsessions -->
      <div class="bg-accent-50 dark:bg-accent-950 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-accent-200 dark:border-accent-800">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-accent-900 dark:text-accent-100 mb-4">
          currently obsessed with:
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400"></span>
            <span class="text-accent-800 dark:text-accent-200">startups</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400"></span>
            <span class="text-accent-800 dark:text-accent-200">learning</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400"></span>
            <span class="text-accent-800 dark:text-accent-200">writing essays</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400"></span>
            <span class="text-accent-800 dark:text-accent-200">training for ironman</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Life Philosophy -->
      <div class="bg-warm-50 dark:bg-warm-950 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-warm-200 dark:border-warm-800">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 dark:text-warm-100 mb-4">
          what drives me:
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-warm-800 dark:text-warm-200">
          <p>"figure it out" mentality</p>
          <p>nth order of thinking</p>
          <p>the 0 multiplier effect</p>
          <p>results</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Fun Fact -->
      <div class="bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-700">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-3">
          random fact:
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-300 leading-relaxed">
          i launched a charity in grade 7 after watching people i love get cancer, scaled it 10x, and have been sailing since 12 but still can't drive.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 